Business Rules

Each person can be a part of many groups or no groups, but each group must have at least one person
Each person must have one or many donations, and each donation must have one or many people
Each donation must be money or an item
A donated item must be connected to an event item, and each event item may have one or many items
Money may be connected to an event, and each event may have one or many donated money
Each group must have one or many events, and each event must have one or many groups
Each email may be connected to many groups and each group may have many emails
Each email must be connected to one and only one event, but each event may have many emails
